query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(d l o s c) */ select c.c_nation,
s.s_nation,
d.d_year,
sum(l.l_revenue) AS revenue
from supplier AS s
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND s.s_region = 'ASIA'
inner join orders AS o
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
inner join date AS d
on o.o_orderdate = d.d_datekey AND d.d_year >= 1992 AND d.d_year <= 1997
inner join customer AS c
on o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND c.c_region = 'ASIA' group by c.c_nation, s.s_nation, d.d_year order by d.d_year asc, revenue desc;
